Description :


Cubase 5 - advanced system for creating music

The composition of Cubase 5 includes fully integrated tools for working with loops (loops), drums and vocals, such as LoopMash and VariAudio, which, combined with composition features and the first VST3 convolution reverb to take musical creativity to new heights. With stunning innovations and additional enhancements that boost productivity and performance

___________________________________________________________

Size: 177.44 MB (unpacked)
Version: 5.1.1
Developer: Steinberg
Bit depth: 32bit
Language: English

System Requirements:
2 GHz CPU (dual core CPU recommended)
1024 MB RAM

                ____________________________________________________



Instructions:

This is a portable app. Run the .exe in the folder after have extracted the archive.

32-bit Plugins (VST2,VST3) do work on this release.

-Working if you drag it in a portable device (stick,hard drive).
I advise you to chose Asio4All as your audio driver
